# omid.dev

Read `AGENTS.md` at the repository root for build commands, layout, and workflow.

This is a Hugo static site (`hugo.yaml`, theme `themes/omid-dev`). No npm/Node build.

- Keep changes minimal and focused.
- Do not commit `public/`, `resources/`, or secrets.
- Only create git commits when the user explicitly asks.
- Run `hugo --minify` after template or config changes; fix build errors before finishing.
